{"tid":234710,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【大雨警報】與一道低壓槽相關的雷雨區正靠近本港（2017/5/8）","createTime":"2017-05-08T13:09:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-10T11:58:18.000Z","uid":38255,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e772a7fdccb87a8126f8c7f9d9baac44e36617df","tid":234710,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T13:09:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><img src=\"http://x.co/wk011\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2Fwk011&h=231cb168&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://x.co/wk012\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2Fwk012&h=31a91e86&s={SIZE}\" /> <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>大雨警報：2017年5月8日</ins></span></span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">此帖文討論期：大雨影響完結為止</span></span></strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n【註】 發出大雨警報，表示本港大部分地區可能受持續大雨影響。　此帖文為短期性質，當取消大雨警報後會隨即停用。　為使大家有一個良好舒適的瀏覽環境，請不要使用簡體中文貼文、提及力場或洗版，謝謝合作。　請勿直接張貼會自動更新的氣象圖片，請把圖片上傳至儲存空間後再轉貼在貼文上。謝謝。　以下圖片會自動更新。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">氣象台專頁現已登場</span><br />\r\n<img src=\"http://x.co/FBlike\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2FFBlike&h=5fdd3157&s={SIZE}\" /><a href=\"http://fb.com/HKGweather\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2FHKGweather&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJmxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=4cb1aa0b\" target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/HKGweather</a><br />\r\n<img src=\"http://x.co/TWlike\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2FTWlike&h=e9b064ef&s={SIZE}\" /><a href=\"http://twitter.com/HKGweather\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHKGweather&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJmxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=58835092\" target=\"_blank\">http://twitter.com/HKGweather</a></span></em><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>◤參考網頁</ins></span></span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n◆ 實時天氣照片：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/ts/index_c_webcam.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fwxinfo%2Fts%2Findex_c_webcam.htm&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJmxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=4dc4c11a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/ts/index_c_webcam.htm</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\n◆ 香港雷達圖像：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/radars/radarc.htm?pv_mode=playback\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fwxinfo%2Fradars%2Fradarc.htm%3Fpv_mode%3Dplayback&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJmxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=a38ac0c7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/radars/radarc.htm?pv_mode=playback</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\n◆ 深圳雷達圖像：<a href=\"http://www.szmb.gov.cn/article/QiXiangJianCe/LeiDaTuXiang\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.szmb.gov.cn%2Farticle%2FQiXiangJianCe%2FLeiDaTuXiang&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJmxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=3dba9a66\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.szmb.gov.cn/article/QiXiangJianCe/LeiDaTuXiang</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\n◆ 東莞雷達圖像：<a href=\"http://www.dg121.com/pda/leida_new.asp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dg121.com%2Fpda%2Fleida_new.asp&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJmxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=48893cb6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.dg121.com/pda/leida_new.asp</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\n◆ 中國雷達圖像：<a href=\"http://www.weather.com.cn/static/html/product_ld.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.weather.com.cn%2Fstatic%2Fhtml%2Fproduct_ld.shtml&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJmxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=da6a7926\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.weather.com.cn/static/html/product_ld.shtml</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\n◆ ECMWF數值預報：<a href=\"http://x.co/ECMWF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2FECMWF&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJmxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=63540c65\" target=\"_blank\">http://x.co/ECMWF</a><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"http://pda.weather.gov.hk/TC_GD_CG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpda.weather.gov.hk%2FTC_GD_CG.jpg&h=c987a128&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://pda.weather.gov.hk/TC_HK_CG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpda.weather.gov.hk%2FTC_HK_CG.jpg&h=28ebca9f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\r\n▲ 雲對地閃電<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"http://pda.weather.gov.hk/TC_GD_CC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpda.weather.gov.hk%2FTC_GD_CC.jpg&h=4dcdafd2&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://pda.weather.gov.hk/TC_HK_CC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpda.weather.gov.hk%2FTC_HK_CC.jpg&h=aca1c465&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\r\n▲ 雲間閃電<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"http://m.weather.gov.hk/image/radar_scale.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.weather.gov.hk%2Fimage%2Fradar_scale.jpg&h=087d95fd&s={SIZE}\" />　　<img src=\"http://pda.weather.gov.hk/radar/rad_256_320/rad256_6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpda.weather.gov.hk%2Fradar%2Frad_256_320%2Frad256_6.jpg&h=f7ca0de3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\r\n<img src=\"http://pda.weather.gov.hk/radar/rad_128_320/rad128_6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpda.weather.gov.hk%2Fradar%2Frad_128_320%2Frad128_6.jpg&h=7755f1ee&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://pda.weather.gov.hk/radar/rad_064_320/rad064_6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpda.weather.gov.hk%2Fradar%2Frad_064_320%2Frad064_6.jpg&h=b6cc5a94&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\r\n▲ 256／128／64公里雷達<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"http://j.mp/17ZL86E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2F17ZL86E&h=0d2cca10&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://j.mp/1g89r7M\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2F1g89r7M&h=05f7fb79&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\r\n▲ 雷達和閃電疊加圖</strong>"},{"pid":"f71a372e0236295d1269d6099fb0839b1e793105","tid":234710,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T13:09:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">由於lihkg app無法載入自動更新圖最新圖像，請選擇以瀏覽器模式觀看圖片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"f146a19d1e510cab9c27bc8247cf887bf1316c21","tid":234710,"uid":56537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T13:11:42.000Z","msg":"屌你！！ 10點放工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fb77a9a923a0aa3ddca9ac15dd029a07120d389","tid":234710,"uid":44630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T13:13:02.000Z","msg":"綠茶留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bdc6664b8b517f584f7cfd9292d0abad0914f26","tid":234710,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T13:13:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b54c14e0e825b45bd45680d81dd992ca2615e965","tid":234710,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T13:13:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">由於lihkg app無法載入自動更新圖最新圖像，請選擇以瀏覽器模式觀看圖片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />hko雷達得左啦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aeee2f0c5b434921b303d3e821803f3b237418b","tid":234710,"uid":51148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T13:15:02.000Z","msg":"乜雨都無"},{"pid":"efc15df680a39dbabc1858464a072f0e57cbaa4b","tid":234710,"uid":35882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T13:15:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf58994585dce5b279060e3b2f3dca9e6b6f09a4","tid":234710,"uid":106336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T13:17:39.000Z","msg":"其實有咩原因爆雨區？<br />\n氣溫太高？ <br />\n嗰陣14年3月30都係因為咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77ddace28af702beff3f6626236a81da0dd2794b","tid":234710,"uid":44630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T13:21:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜雨都無</blockquote><br />\n大約10點先會影響香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71b76b08be4977146d2c752139a38faa5a528be7","tid":234710,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T13:22:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實有咩原因爆雨區？<br />\n氣溫太高？ <br />\n嗰陣14年3月30都係因為咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁大範圍係低壓槽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n330都係低壓槽"},{"pid":"912f7d7797caa7abc927b5484d2170c4b69ecb4f","tid":234710,"uid":36650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T13:28:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zDjmhGH0sQ0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzDjmhGH0sQ0&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJmxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=809c2c79\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zDjmhGH0sQ0</a><br />\n<br />\n【大雨預警】08/05/2017<br />\n<br />\n【大雨預警】本台於2017年5月8日2030時向全港各區發出大雨預警。請各位出門前密切留意天氣訊息，並攜備雨具。 <br />\n<br />\n【天氣概況】廣東北部的一道雷雨帶正穩定南下，與其相關嘅雨區將於稍後影響香港。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09489e9a60c06ad9427afedc177af0d410a2cf9a","tid":234710,"uid":9800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T13:30:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">It's coming </span></span>"},{"pid":"3a346a5fb8d1bf96323d07c75c9d4c4e328df9a8","tid":234710,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T13:32:13.000Z","msg":"我想知係影響幾耐左右？"},{"pid":"a1d7de19e7716cac37a8b069253a949da9ed2ce7","tid":234710,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T13:33:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想知係影響幾耐左右？</blockquote><br />\n天光前一定冇雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98ce6483c7948689ab8f55c18f0cbd9e00c6ba0e","tid":234710,"uid":44630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T13:49:59.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">特別天氣提示</span></span></strong><br />\n一道雷雨帶正橫過珠江口一帶，並可能會在未來一兩小時影響本港。市民請提高警惕。 (08-05-2017 21:45)"},{"pid":"70a193db8c086af0213472256bc1db7a9a76e3f2","tid":234710,"uid":6959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T13:56:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c6aab1f665a9b4e90df76416755de58e4a5f52b9","tid":234710,"uid":44630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T13:57:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開始未？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n比多一陣應該會到大西北<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5fd84e9231fea9e10b05a4da4d9497fcde820ac","tid":234710,"uid":106336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T14:06:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實有咩原因爆雨區？<br />\n氣溫太高？ <br />\n嗰陣14年3月30都係因為咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁大範圍係低壓槽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n330都係低壓槽</blockquote><br />\n原來係咁<br />\n但係之前香港都試過有爆出少量雨區又點解？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11f3c10f9b7a0ab291ec22e1310383f8953537d9","tid":234710,"uid":43178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T14:09:11.000Z","msg":"雷暴警告<br />\n<br />\n天文台在5月8日下午10時正發出雷暴警告，有效時間至明日下午11時30分，預料香港有幾陣狂風雷暴。預料高達每小時70公里或以上的陣風吹襲香港。<br />\n<br />\n雷暴發生時，請採取以下預防措施：<br />\n<br />\n1.留在室內。在室外的人士應躲入建築物內。<br />\n<br />\n2.切勿站立於高地或接近導電的物體、樹木或桅杆。<br />\n<br />\n3.提防猛烈陣風。留心被飛散或墜落物件擊中。<br />\n<br />\n4.在高速公路或天橋上的駕車人士應減低車速，提防猛烈陣風吹襲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以上天氣稿由天文台於2017年05月08日22時00分發出"},{"pid":"e02ef566b0cebd62f217556530d4325c3a854941","tid":234710,"uid":38255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T14:09:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實有咩原因爆雨區？<br />\n氣溫太高？ <br />\n嗰陣14年3月30都係因為咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁大範圍係低壓槽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n330都係低壓槽</blockquote><br />\n原來係咁<br />\n但係之前香港都試過有爆出少量雨區又點解？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n細雨區通常係高溫熱對流（通常黃紅），<br />\n可以係地型雨（藍綠回波多）<br />\n仲有大型不穩定系統係附近（例如低壓槽或颱風靠近），可以激發境內自產雨區"},{"pid":"ca29d4c826af163d59bf7ea198a77db5a730d8fb","tid":234710,"uid":44630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T14:11:33.000Z","msg":"有無大西北居民報告下開波未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"025ea511b27ffcb926b859c44dd4a53606131939","tid":234710,"uid":50790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T14:11:43.000Z","msg":"一睇到呢個po 即落雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6a577e8fa03c27d299b92f5ed637db9546805c8","tid":234710,"uid":50513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T14:16:53.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"00f519504c449c6d751afa564fcb716e74d529d3","tid":234710,"uid":7123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T14:17:06.000Z","msg":"九龍無雨"},